      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation scenarios share geometry, fluid, flow regime, and boundary condition similarity with the intended CPB use scenario.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry under bovine blood analog at Reynolds numbers matching CPB conditions. Rotational speed and flow rate ranges overlap with clinical CPB operating envelope. Geometric and dynamic similarity criteria met for MRL 2."
    },
