      "rationale": "At MRL 2, explicit solver error quantification beyond iterative convergence monitoring is not required. Residuals reduced by six orders of magnitude; mass imbalance below 0.01%. Scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 at MRL 2."
