    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 for MRL 2 Class II device context. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model is fit for purpose to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in CPB applications. Output comparison factor exceeds required level (achieved 3, required 2), providing additional confidence margin. Assessment team unanimously accepts the simulation credibility package.",
